    <h5>Skills</h5>
    <p>Bite (active): 
        <span class="move-description"> This monster can leave nasty bite wounds.</span>
    </p>
    <p>Shadow hand (active):
        <span class="move-description"> The monster can manipulate the shadows to attack their opponents.</span>
    </p>
    <p>Strength in Darkness (passive):
        <span class="move-description"> When in darkness, the skivverlings' sorc skill goes up to 12. 
            Any dark damage it takes is halved, regardless of environment.</span>
    </p>
    <p>Blinded by the Light (passive):
        <span class="move-description"> When in light areas, the skivverlings' sorc skill is 4. 
            Any light damage it takes is doubled, regardless of environment.
        </span>
    </p>

    <p>Run in groups of 7.</p>
